==English==
===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[igneous]] [[rock]]'''
#{{geology}} one of the major groups of rock that makes up the [[crust]] of the [[Earth]]; formed by the [[cooling]] of [[molten]] rock, either below the [[surface]] ([[intrusve]]) or on the surface ([[extrusive]])
